Oscar Quitak https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oscar_Quitak 0 Oscar Quitak (born 10 March 1926) is a British film and television actor. His television credits include: Z-Cars, Man in a Suitcase, Doomwatch, Ace of Wands, Colditz, The Changes, The New Avengers, Open All Hours, Kessler as Josef Mengele, Chessgame, Howards' Way, A Very British Coup, Yes, Prime Minister, Saracen, Lovejoy and Telltale. He lives with his wife, the actress Andree Melly, on Ibiza. Oscar_Quitak ( born_10_March_1926 ) is a_British_film_and_television_actor .
